---
// src/components/Recognition.astro
// ──────────────────────────────────
// Seção de Reconhecimento e Mídia — Layout editorial premium
---

<section id="recognition" class="section reveal-section">
  <div class="container">

    <header class="section-header">
      <span class="section-index">03</span>
      <h2 data-i18n="recognition.title">Impacto &amp; Mídia</h2>
    </header>

    <div class="recognition-grid">

      <!-- Featured: NASA Global Win -->
      <div class="recognition-card featured reveal-item" style="--delay: 0s">
        <div class="card-visual">
          <img src="/assets/images/recognition_nasa.png" alt="NASA Recognition" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="card-content">
          <span class="card-tag label">Global Award</span>
          <h3 data-i18n="recognition.nasa.title">NASA Space Apps Global Winner</h3>
          <p data-i18n="recognition.nasa.text">Vencedor mundial com o projeto Poseidon, uma solução de IA que utiliza Redes Neurais Convolucionais (Deep Learning) e imagens de satélite do tipo SAR (Radar de Abertura Sintética) para identificar manchas de óleo nos oceanos mesmo através de nuvens ou à noite. Desenvolvido em resposta ao desastre ambiental de 2019 no Brasil, o sistema automatiza o monitoramento marítimo global, reduzindo drasticamente o tempo de resposta para mitigar impactos ecológicos e econômicos.</p>
          <div class="card-links">
            <a href="https://2019.spaceappschallenge.org/challenges/living-our-world/smash-your-sdgs/teams/massa/" target="_blank" class="link-item">Projeto NASA</a>
            <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w-gaVI9TczY" target="_blank" class="link-item">Ver Vídeo</a>
            <a href="https://agenciabrasil.ebc.com.br/geral/noticia/2020-01/brasileiros-ganham-concurso-de-solucoes-tecnologicas-da-nasa" target="_blank" class="link-item">Agência Brasil</a>
            <a href="https://www.dw.com/pt-br/brasileiros-recebem-pr%C3%AAmio-da-nasa-por-projeto-de-ia/a-65178679" target="_blank" class="link-item">DW News</a>
            <a href="https://g1.globo.com/sp/mogi-das-cruzes-suzano/noticia/2020/02/07/equipe-de-mogiana-desenvolve-inteligencia-artificial-para-detectar-manchas-de-oleo-e-vence-concurso-da-nasa.ghtml" target="_blank" class="link-item">G1 Globo</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Featured: IBM C0D3RS with Image -->
      <div class="recognition-card reveal-item" style="--delay: 0.1s">
        <div class="card-visual">
          <img src="/assets/images/C0D3RS_Championship.png" alt="IBM C0D3RS Championship" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
        <div class="card-content">
          <div class="card-tags">
            <span class="card-tag label">Prime Video &amp; IBM</span>
            <span class="card-tag label">Reality Show</span>
          </div>
          <h3 data-i18n="recognition.ibm.title">C0D3RS Championship</h3>
          <p data-i18n="recognition.ibm.text">Finalista representando o Brasil na minissérie exclusiva da IBM e Prime Video. Uma competição épica entre os melhores desenvolvedores da América Latina, utilizando IBM Cloud e IA para resolver problemas reais da sociedade em um formato de reality show tecnológico.</p>
          <div class="card-links">
            <a href="https://www.primevideo.com/detail/C0d3rs-Championship/0GS98CG03BVM7C224YK7KIWXOJ" target="_blank" class="link-item">Assistir no Prime</a>
            <a href="https://www.eluniverso.com/entretenimiento/television/los-desarrolladores-compiten-por-llegar-a-la-final-en-c0d3rs-championship-de-amazon-prime-video-nota/" target="_blank" class="link-item">Sobre a Série</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Featured: Podcasts/Interviews with Spotify Embed -->
      <div class="recognition-card reveal-item" style="--delay: 0.2s">
        <div class="card-visual podcast-embed" style="background: #121212; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; height: 232px; aspect-ratio: auto;">
          <iframe 
            style="border-radius:0" 
            src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/episode/4jdimruOz6KDv1j7Xj9KS6?utm_source=generator&theme=0" 
            width="100%" 
            height="232" 
            frameBorder="0" 
            allowfullscreen="" 
            allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" 
            loading="lazy">
          </iframe>
        </div>
        <div class="card-content">
          <span class="card-tag label">Podcast Alura</span>
          <h3 data-i18n="recognition.media.title">Talks &amp; Deep Dives</h3>
          <p data-i18n="recognition.media.text">Discussões profundas no Hipsters Ponto Tech sobre Hackathons da NASA e IA para detecção de óleo no mar.</p>
          <div class="card-links">
            <a href="https://www.alura.com.br/podcast/hackathons-nasa-e-manchas-de-oleo-hipsters-ponto-tech-178-a387" target="_blank" class="link-item">Ver na Alura</a>
            <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O9uXr5s8-CY" target="_blank" class="link-item">YouTube</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Featured: EducaXperience YouTube Embed -->
      <div class="recognition-card reveal-item" style="--delay: 0.3s">
        <div class="card-visual youtube-embed">
          <iframe 
            width="100%" 
            height="100%" 
            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ppB_1756qcI" 
            title="Como a Tecnologia nos levou à Nasa? | EducaXperience" 
            frameborder="0" 
            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" 
            allowfullscreen>
          </iframe>
        </div>
        <div class="card-content">
          <span class="card-tag label">Keynote Talk</span>
          <h3 data-i18n="recognition.talk.title">Jornada até a NASA</h3>
          <p data-i18n="recognition.talk.text">Palestra completa no EducaXperience sobre tecnologia, inovação e os bastidores da vitória global.</p>
          <div class="card-links">
            <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ppB_1756qcI" target="_blank" class="link-item">Assistir no YouTube</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Featured: Digital Innovation Video Embed -->
      <div class="recognition-card reveal-item" style="--delay: 0.4s">
        <div class="card-visual youtube-embed">
          <iframe 
            width="100%" 
            height="100%" 
            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/O9uXr5s8-CY" 
            title="Eduardo Ritter - Tech & Innovation" 
            frameborder="0" 
            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" 
            allowfullscreen>
          </iframe>
        </div>
        <div class="card-content">
          <span class="card-tag label">Community &amp; Tech</span>
          <h3 data-i18n="recognition.media.video2.title">Inovação na Prática</h3>
          <p data-i18n="recognition.media.video2.text">Entrevista técnica e insights sobre o desenvolvimento de produtos digitais e o ecossistema de tecnologia.</p>
          <div class="card-links">
            <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O9uXr5s8-CY" target="_blank" class="link-item">Ver Vídeo Completo</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .recognition-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 32px;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }

  .recognition-card {
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform 0.4s var(--ease), border-color 0.4s var(--ease);
  }

  .recognition-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    border-color: var(--border-hover);
  }

  /* Card Visual Section */
  .card-visual {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: #000;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .card-visual img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.6s var(--ease);
  }

  .recognition-card:hover .card-visual img {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .youtube-embed {
    position: relative;
    background: #000;
  }

  /* Content Section */
  .card-content {
    padding: 32px;
    flex-grow: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .recognition-card.featured {
    grid-column: span 2;
    flex-direction: row;
  }

  .recognition-card.featured .card-visual {
    width: 55%;
    height: auto;
    aspect-ratio: unset;
    border-bottom: none;
    border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .recognition-card.featured .card-content {
    width: 45%;
    background: var(--text-1);
    color: var(--bg);
  }

  .recognition-card.featured .card-tag,
  .recognition-card.featured .link-item,
  .recognition-card.featured p {
    color: var(--bg);
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .recognition-card.featured h3 {
    color: var(--bg);
  }

  .recognition-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 2.5vw, 2.2rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    margin: 12px 0 16px;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .recognition-card p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--text-2);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .card-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  .link-item {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    transition: all 0.3s var(--ease);
  }

  .link-item:hover {
    background: var(--text-1);
    color: var(--bg);
    border-color: var(--text-1);
  }

  .recognition-card.featured .link-item {
    border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
  }

  .recognition-card.featured .link-item:hover {
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text-1);
    border-color: var(--bg);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .recognition-card.featured {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .recognition-card.featured .card-visual,
    .recognition-card.featured .card-content {
      width: 100%;
    }
    .recognition-card.featured .card-visual {
      border-right: none;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .recognition-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
    }
    .card-content {
      padding: 24px;
    }
    .recognition-card h3 {
      font-size: 1.6rem;
    }
  }
</style>
